@page
@model MSIS4363devopstools.Pages.JenkinsModel
@{
}
<div class="jenkinspage">
    <div class="text-center roboto">
        <h1>Jenkins Evaluation Report</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="row my-5 simplebox roboto">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <img src="~/devopstoolspictures/jenkins-logo.png" class="chatimage d-block img-fluid mx-auto" />
        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-6 orangebox">
            <h2>What I Like (+)</h2>
            <p>(+) Free and open-source</p>
            <p>(+) Clean, easy-to-navigate web interface</p>
            <p>(+) Highly flexible and customizable through plugins and scripting</p>
            <p>(+) Integrates well with tools like GitHub, .NET, and PowerShell</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row my-5 simplebox roboto">
        <div class="col-sm-6 orangebox">
            <h2>Could Be Better (-)</h2>
            <p>(-) Limited and unclear installation guidance for Windows environments</p>
            <p>(-) Difficult to configure as a Windows service under enterprise security and GPO policies</p>
            <p>(-) Requires external tools (like NSSM) for reliable service management and auto-start</p>
            <p>(-) Steep learning curve for automating post-build steps such as service restarts</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 simplebox">
            <img src="~/devopstoolspictures/jenkins-logo.png" class="chatimage d-block img-fluid mx-auto mt-1" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row my-5 simplebox roboto">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <img src="~/devopstoolspictures/jenkins-logo.png" class="chatimage d-block img-fluid mx-auto" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 orangebox ratings">
            <h2>Ratings</h2>
            <p>Overall Rating: <b>7.5</b></p>
            <p>Ease of Use: <b>7/10</b></p>
            <p>Perceived Usefulness for Student Projects: <b>9/10</b></p>
            <p>Cost/Pricing Tiers: <b>10/10</b> (completely free)</p>
            <p>Features: <b>8/10</b></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5 simplebox roboto">
        <div class="orangebox text-start">
            <h2>Overall Recommendation</h2>
            <p>
                Jenkins is a powerful, flexible automation tool that’s well-suited for student projects focused on DevOps, CI/CD, and software deployment. Its web interface is simple and clean, making daily use intuitive. However, the setup process—especially on Windows—is challenging, with limited official documentation and compatibility issues under enterprise restrictions. Setting up Jenkins to run reliably as a background service required third-party solutions like NSSM and carefully written batch scripts to handle restarts after builds.
            </p>
            <p>
                Despite those hurdles, Jenkins remains one of the best free options for students learning automation pipelines and system integration. It teaches valuable troubleshooting and scripting skills, making it a strong recommendation for hands-on technical projects.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>